  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/806970/extras/6cb1c7d385a7256e8a2a4029d0443ac6.avif?t=1530302141\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description:</h2>Loader is an exciting puzzle game where you place loads on platforms to pass levels. <br>In this game you have to correctly place the loads onto platforms to pass the levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/806970/extras/6c3415da7ff4a60c8f64554b1e4d9fb8.avif?t=1530302141\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> More than 15 exciting levels<br></li><li> Ability to change textures<br></li><li> Level editor<br></li><li> Adding levels other players made<br></li><li> Adding your own textures, as well as other players textures<br></li><li> Steam Achievements</li></ul>",
